    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but it feels like you're being kind of middle of the road. some people say the UN is basically just a failed relic that's actually making things worse by giving legitimacy to dictators who ignore them. do historians actually think the UN has any real legitimacy left, or is that just a nice way of looking at it?",
